    public static enum GeoFusionEnrichmentOperator.GeoFusionAction
extends java.lang.Enum<GeoFusionEnrichmentOperator.GeoFusionAction>
    Geospatial fusion actions:
    • takeA always use geometry from first model
    • takeB always use geometry from second model, if ambiguous take most detailed
    • takeAll merge all geometries
    • takeMostDetailed use most detailed geometry from any model, e.g., in terms of lexical length of latitude and longitude values
